{"tid":628386,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[召喚紅袍白頭佬巴打]有無人回味下鬼泣系列","createTime":"2018-04-13T19:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T11:52:32.000Z","uid":5375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9c95d150c1366e8b4910291ca3737801c5d21ff1","tid":628386,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T19:35:58.000Z","msg":"原來上個月係STEAM發行左DEVIL MAY CRY 123 HD COLLECTION，值就一定唔值，但未玩過12代，或者用黎收藏就另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3代就肯定公認最好玩，故事、人物、操作都大幅超越前作，但丁又夠晒寸嘴。而COMBO系統係本作成為DMC系列既主要特色，<br />\n<br />\n而4代同DMC除左畫面係時代上有正常既技術進步外，只有係COMBO方面叫做有D誠意，但都可以話係無任何突破。其他元素唔洗講，全部炒冷飯，<br />\n<br />\n4代前後10關關卡既路線同BOSS一樣，已經屌到上天，故事方面你老未，竟然係王子公主英雄救美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDMC係REBOOT作就唔評了，如果視作一隻新GAME絕對唔錯既<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/04CJBGM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F04CJBGM.jpg&h=172f6681&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63aca323e474681a707850b509033ce8f4bef498","tid":628386,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T19:52:01.000Z","msg":"漏左講，戰鬥BGM都係一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca288cd62b815e1fd9c45844ee040801eec5b0b","tid":628386,"uid":114094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T21:40:38.000Z","msg":"第一隻DMC 係IOS 上邊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知邊集，有得用手槍"},{"pid":"3f46f9e5e09d4b8ef1511190f066f7a67ec50c32","tid":628386,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T00:29:49.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1fa72200ac75ea5a10c61a5b04d4e937a41e09b1","tid":628386,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ca288cd62b815e1fd9c45844ee040801eec5b0b","tid":628386,"uid":